        <description>&lt;p&gt;Hugo-theme-jane optimized for footnote. When you mouse hover the footnote&lt;sup class=&#34;footnote-ref&#34; id=&#34;fnref:example&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#fn:example&#34;&gt;1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt; , footnote content will be displayed.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&#34;install&#34;&gt;Install&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;You can create footnotes like this&lt;sup class=&#34;footnote-ref&#34; id=&#34;fnref:Install&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#fn:Install&#34;&gt;2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;.
init a folder&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;snap install hugo --channel=extended
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&#34;init&#34;&gt;Init&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;You can create footnotes like this&lt;sup class=&#34;footnote-ref&#34; id=&#34;fnref:Init&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#fn:Init&#34;&gt;3&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;hugo new site leone-website
 cd leone-website
 git clone https://github.com/xianmin/hugo-theme-jane.git --depth=1 themes/jane
 cp -r themes/jane/exampleSite/content ./
 cp themes/jane/exampleSite/config.toml ./
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
